title: Tinashe Muchawaya
summary: Tinashe Muchawaya (born 3 April 1997) is a Zimbabwean cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Rising Stars in the 2017–18 Logan Cup on 19 April 2018. He made his List A debut for Rising Stars in the 2017–18 Pro50 Championship on 29 April 2018. In December 2020, he was selected to play for the Mountaineers in the 2020–21 Logan Cup.
